      "replay": "An exact decision_id plus identical canonical envelope is an idempotent duplicate with no second state change or outbox fact. The same decision_id with a different envelope is a security conflict and is rejected and audited. Uniqueness scope is repository_id plus request_id plus request_generation."
    }
  },
